---
title: Parmesan and Herb Crusted Cod with Buttery Potatoes and Carrots
description: Flaky fish gets a crunchy twist with an Italian seasoning, panko, and Parmesan crust. Sweet carrots and hearty potatoes are tossed with butter and parsley to keep you satisfied (and away from the snack drawer later).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/parmesan-and-herb-crusted-fish-1f97440f.jpg
